0.1.name: wordpress/pgnviewer-plugin
0.1.description: A simple plugin that allows you to embed ChessTempo's PGNViewer into a post or page to show chess games from PGN format files. USAGE: While editing a post, create a custom field with key PGN and paste the URL of the PGN file into the Value field.
